{
  "texts": [
    "One area of concern may be researcher biasness.",
    "To reduce threats in interpretation, this was mitigated by ensuring that no papers written by authors were included in the 370 primary papers evaluated.",
    "Further, an independent external reviewer played a crucial role in ensuring the validity and accuracy of the classifications.",
    "In addition to auditing the methodology and data extraction process, the reviewer also examined the accuracy of paper classifications, both from the automated process and the subsequent manual verification.",
    "Any discrepancies identified were addressed, and the classification model was refined accordingly."
  ]
}